00:20:48,781 --> 00:20:51,565
We have a long-standing
salsa appointment tonight,

484
00:20:51,633 --> 00:20:54,418
and... Sorry.
You're on your own.

485
00:20:54,487 --> 00:20:56,332
Right. I bet it's gonna be long.

486
00:20:56,356 --> 00:20:58,183
Mmm-hmm. Real long.

487
00:20:58,207 --> 00:21:00,207
She's almost finished.

488
00:21:00,275 --> 00:21:02,020
She has read all of your
charts and none of mine.

489
00:21:02,044 --> 00:21:03,472
Yeah, I found her.
I brought her here.

490
00:21:03,496 --> 00:21:06,264
Lex, can you take a look
at some of my cases, too?

491
00:21:06,332 --> 00:21:08,866
Or not. I mean, it's
fine if you don't want to.

492
00:21:08,935 --> 00:21:10,817
It's okay. I can. I will...

493
00:21:10,886 --> 00:21:14,638
No, no, no, no, you will not.
Not until she's finished with mine.

494
00:21:14,707 --> 00:21:16,819
Okay, these take
priority, Lexie.

495
00:21:16,843 --> 00:21:18,363
You don't need
Lexie. You got Torres.

496
00:21:18,427 --> 00:21:20,088
They're for Cristina.
She's not even here.

497
00:21:20,112 --> 00:21:21,356
Which is why she needs the help.

498
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:22,758
She does not need the help.

499
00:21:22,782 --> 00:21:24,293
She just needs to finish
mine. And you know what?

500
00:21:24,317 --> 00:21:25,317
Shh!

501
00:21:29,372 --> 00:21:32,256
Yeah, but you know what?
There is no compromise.

502
00:21:32,325 --> 00:21:34,491
You don't have half a baby.

